===================================================================================
REQUIRED LIBRARIES
===================================================================================

In order to install those libraries, you also need to install autoconf and automake tools on 
your machine (on Ubuntu just say: sudo apt-get install automake autoconf).

"libantlr3c-3.2.tar.gz" is the ANTLR library prerequisite for the tool
(details of installing this library can be found in its directory)

You can use the following commands to install:

	tar -xvzf libantlr3c-3.2.tar.gz
	cd libantlr3c-3.2
	(for 32bit machine ./configure)
	(for 64bit machine ./configure --enable-64bit)
	make 
	sudo make install

----------------------------------------------------------

"libroxml-2.2.3.tar.gz" is the XML parser library.

The following commands to install this library:

	tar -xvzf libroxml-2.2.3.tar.gz
	cd libroxml-2.2.3
	make 
	sudo make install 
